项目应用脚手架
1.安装node.js和npm环境---https://www.cnblogs.com/hcfinal/p/9480481.html
···
 安装结果：
    C:\Users\wangtingtao>node -v
    v12.18.3

    C:\Users\wangtingtao>npm -v
    6.14.6
 配置node、和npm
    执行npm install cluster
    ···
        npm WARN saveError ENOENT: no such file or directory, open 'C:\Users\wangtingtao\package.json'
        npm notice created a lockfile as package-lock.json. You should commit this file.
        npm WARN enoent ENOENT: no such file or directory, open 'C:\Users\wangtingtao\package.json'
        npm WARN wangtingtao No description
        npm WARN wangtingtao No repository field.
        npm WARN wangtingtao No README data
        npm WARN wangtingtao No license field.
    ···
    修改node.js文件目录配置
        1.D盘新增\nodejs\node_global \nodejs\node_cache 文件夹
        2.执行如下命令
        ···
            C:\Users\wangtingtao>npm config set prefix "D:\nodejs\node_global"

            C:\Users\wangtingtao>npm config set cache "D:\nodejs\node_cache"
        ···
        3.执行命令npm install cluster -g
        ···
            C:\Users\wangtingtao>npm install cluster -g
            + cluster@0.7.7
            added 14 packages from 2 contributors in 51.084s
        ···
     修改环境信息变量
        1.新增NODE_PATH = D:\nodejs\node_global\node_modules
        2.修改之前的npm配置path=C:\Users\wangtingtao\AppData\Roaming\npm
        修改为：path= D:\nodejs\node_global
        3.重启命令行执行 node、require('cluster')
        ···
            > require('cluster')
            EventEmitter {
              _events: [Object: null prototype] {},
              _eventsCount: 0,
              _maxListeners: undefined,
              isWorker: false,
              isMaster: true,
              Worker: [Function: Worker],
              workers: {},
              settings: {},
              SCHED_NONE: 1,
              SCHED_RR: 2,
              schedulingPolicy: 1,
              setupMaster: [Function],
              fork: [Function],
              disconnect: [Function],
              [Symbol(kCapture)]: false
            }
            >
        ···
        4.将npm的模块下载仓库从默认的国外站点改为国内的站点
        ···
            C:\Users\wangtingtao>npm --registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org install cluster
            npm WARN saveError ENOENT: no such file or directory, open 'C:\Users\wangtingtao\package.json'
            npm WARN enoent ENOENT: no such file or directory, open 'C:\Users\wangtingtao\package.json'
            npm WARN wangtingtao No description
            npm WARN wangtingtao No repository field.
            npm WARN wangtingtao No README data
            npm WARN wangtingtao No license field.

            + cluster@0.7.7
            updated 1 package in 0.617s
        ···
        如果想一直使用这个源的地址，那么可以使用下面这个命令来配置。
        npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org
        ···
            C:\Users\wangtingtao>npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org
            npm WARN deprecated request@2.88.2: request has been deprecated, see https://github.com/request/request/issues/3142
            npm WARN deprecated har-validator@5.1.5: this
            D:\nodejs\node_global\cnpm -> D:\nodejs\node_global\node_modules\cnpm\bin\cnpm
            + cnpm@6.1.1
            added 688 packages from 971 contributors in 47.693s
        ···

